<h1 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    🎉 You're Invited to a Talk on Arena!
</h1>

<p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Get ready for an insightful discussion! You've been invited to a talk titled **"{{talkTitle}}"** featuring **{{speakerName}}** on Arena.
</p>

<div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 30px 0; border-left: 4px solid #8e44ad;">
    <h3 style="color: #8e44ad; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">🎙️ Talk Details</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #555; width: 30%;">Talk Title:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #333;">{{talkTitle}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">Speaker:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #333;">{{speakerName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">Date:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #333;">{{talkDate}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">Time:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #333;">{{talkTime}} {{timeZone}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">Topics:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #333;">
                {{#each topics}}
                    <span style="background: #e0e0e0; color: #555; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 15px; font-size: 12px; margin-right: 5px; display: inline-block;">
                        {{this}}
                    </span>
                {{/each}}
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

