        <div style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;">🧠</div>
        <h4 style="color: #667eea; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Engaging Content</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">Dive deep into "software" and "technologies" related discussions.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 200px; background: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;">💡</div>
        <h4 style="color: #856404; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Interactive Q&A</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">Ask questions and get answers directly from the speaker.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 200px; background: #d1ecf1; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;">🌐</div>
        <h4 style="color: #0c5460; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Connect & Network</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">Meet and interact with other like-minded individuals.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{talkUrl}}" style="background: #8e44ad; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
        Join the Talk on Arena
